    "created_at": "2025-05-28T21:33:27Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-05-28T21:33:27Z",
    "body": "Another use case is for dynamic palette generation. If I'm using a tool like `wallust`, I can have it generate a color palette and use that in my main config file.\n\nI also understand I can build a custom wallust config that updates the main config, but the risks of modifying content I don't want to modify is high.",
