    "created_at": "2025-12-20T11:02:15Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-12-20T11:02:15Z",
    "body": "Hi everyone,\n\nthe implementation for this feature request is available in PR [#6894](https://github.com/starship/starship/pull/6894). It already includes:\n- TOML-based merging of multiple config files via STARSHIP_CONFIG\n- Tests for precedence, partial file existence and cross-platform separators\n- Documentation updates and several rounds of review feedback.\n\nSince the original reviewer has stepped back from this PR, would it be possible for another maintainer to take ownership of the review, or let me know if there’s anything blocking it from being merged so I can address it?",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
