    "created_at": "2026-02-24T01:17:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-02-24T07:22:26Z",
    "body": "For those interested in this feature while we await the PR review, I just wrote a tiny program `starship-multi-config` that'll merge starship configs (including a preset if provided) and cache the resulting config. You can use it in your shell init script.\n\nhttps://github.com/sargunv/starship-multi-config\n\nFor example:\n\n```zsh\nexport STARSHIP_CONFIG=\"$(starship-multi-config --preset gruvbox-rainbow ~/.config/starship.d/*.toml)\"\neval \"$(starship init zsh)\"\n```\n\nLooking forward to archiving my repo when this is someday integrated into starship itself!",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
