    "created_at": "2026-04-17T20:12:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-04-17T20:12:26Z",
    "body": "Why is this feature still being ignored?\nThis request has been raised at least a dozen times, and there are several implementations that seem to be uncontroversial.\n\nThis feature is genuinely useful. There’s some sensitive information you simply can’t put in a public repository, and TOML doesn’t offer any way to use includes. \nSeveral more cases where this is necessary are described.\n\nI would like to draw the reviewers' attention to this.",
